    • ProxyThread

      protected ProxyThread(ProxyServer server, Socket socket, HttpSender httpSender)
      Deprecated.
      Constructs a ProxyThread with the given proxy server, socket and HTTP sender.
      Parameters:
      server - the parent proxy server.
      socket - the connected socket to read/write the messages.
      httpSender - the object used to send the messages, might be null in which case a default is used.
      Since:
      2.6.0
